{"id":"2666f31d-6a56-4229-961a-cd90792a668d","name":"Shiroko Terror","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(54, 128, 94)\">Shiroko Terror from Blue Archive</span></strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Anubis, Goddess of Death</span></strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Former Member of the </span></strong><a href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/c162f3df-b0b6-40a3-a6d1-8f0a027e162b_character-foreclosure-taskforce\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><strong><em><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.55)\">Foreclosure Taskforce</span></em></strong></a></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Pre Ark Destruction</span></strong><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/18f39a93-d5ef-4bd8-8438-474f1378a692_2155e634-92e5-4ec3-8bc8-1bd2fce1b523.webp?width=1000\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/18f39a93-d5ef-4bd8-8438-474f1378a692_1a5b5496-e85e-43b8-b864-14ef02f740df.webp?width=1000\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/18f39a93-d5ef-4bd8-8438-474f1378a692_220bbbec-bb66-4dec-98ea-552614c18b62.webp?width=1000\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/18f39a93-d5ef-4bd8-8438-474f1378a692_83c938ee-dcf6-4e31-9728-64af94178cec.webp?width=1000\"><em>\"It is said that their 'Mysteries' will be turned into 'Terrors', with no way to undo it, much like how the dead cannot be resurrected.\"</em><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/18f39a93-d5ef-4b